snippet.title: Stephen King's F13 - game trailer (1999) Macintosh/PC (Windows)
snippet.description:
Stephen King's F13 -  official game trailer
Developed by Presto Studios (USA) on PC (windows) and Macintosh.
Published by Blue Byte Studio GmbH (Europe)  and Blue Byte Software, Inc. (USA).
Distributed in USA by Interplay Entertainment Corp.
Year : 1999  

Trailer Found on the 'Battle Isle - The Andosia War' game disc.
